00:00:32.180 --> 00:00:36.220
But that all changed when researchers like
Jane Goodall realized that chimps use sticks

00:00:36.220 --> 00:00:38.240
as tools to get ants out of logs.

00:00:38.240 --> 00:00:40.540
Suddenly humans didn’t look so smart anymore.

00:00:40.540 --> 00:00:44.472
Scientists consider the corvid family, which
includes crows, magpies, and ravens, some

00:00:44.472 --> 00:00:46.040
of the smartest among birds.

00:00:46.040 --> 00:00:48.600
